#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/license.rst:4
msgid "About Free Software and the GPL"
msgstr "O brezplačnem programju in GPL"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/license.rst:9
msgid ""
"When one hears about \"free software\", the first thing that comes to mind "
"might be \"no cost\". While this is typically true, the term \"free software\" "
"as used by the Free Software Foundation (originators of the GNU Project and "
"creators of the GNU General Public License) is intended to mean \"free as in "
"freedom\" rather than the \"no cost\" sense (which is usually referred to as "
"\"free as in free beer\" or *gratis*). Free software in this sense is software "
"which you are free to use, copy, modify, redistribute, with no limit. Contrast "
"this with the licensing of most commercial software packages, where you are "
"allowed to load the software on a single computer, are allowed to make no "
"copies, and never see the source code. Free software allows incredible freedom "
"to the end user. Since the source code is universally available, there are also "
"many more chances for bugs to be caught and fixed."
msgstr ""
"Čim slišimo ali preberemo izraz \"prosto programje\" (ang. *free software*), "
"najprej pomislimo na \"brezplačno\". Čeprav je to običajno res, izraz \"prosto "
"programje\", kot ga uporablja Free Software Foundation (stvaritelji projekta "
"GNU Project in licence GNU General Public License), pomeni prosto bolj v smislu "
"svobode kot brezplačnega. Prosto programje je torej v tej luči vse programje, "
"ki ga lahko uporabljate, razmnožujete, širite, spreminjate in izboljšujete brez "
"omejitev. Primerjajte to z licenciranjem večine komercialnih programskih "
"paketov, ki dovoljujejo zagon programa na enem samem računalniku, prepovedujejo "
"razmnoževanje in ne dovoljujejo pregleda izvorne kode. Prosto programje omogoča "
"uporabnikom izjemno svobodo. Ker je izvorna koda na vpogled vsem, je tudi več "
"možnosti, da bodo vsakršne napake odkrite in popravljene."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/license.rst:21
msgid "When a program is licensed under the GNU General Public License (the GPL):"
msgstr "Ko je program izdan pod licenco GNU General Public License (GPL):"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/license.rst:23
msgid "You have the right to use the program for any purpose."
msgstr "imate pravico uporabljati ta program za kakršen koli namen,"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/license.rst:24
msgid ""
"You have the right to modify the program and have access to the source codes."
msgstr "imate pravico spreminjati program in dostopati do izvorne kode,"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/license.rst:25
msgid "You have the right to copy and distribute the program."
msgstr "imate pravico kopirati in širiti program,"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/license.rst:26
msgid "You have the right to improve the program, and release your own versions."
msgstr "imate pravico izboljšati program in širiti spremenjeno različico."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/license.rst:28
msgid ""
"In return for these rights, you have some responsibilities if you distribute a "
"GPL'd program, responsibilities that are designed to protect your freedoms and "
"the freedoms of others:"
msgstr ""
"V zameno za te pravice imate tudi nekaj dolžnosti, če širite program z licenco "
"GPL. Dolžnosti, ki ščitijo vašo svobodo in svobodo drugih:"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/license.rst:31
msgid ""
"You must provide a copy of the GPL with the program, so that recipients are "
"aware of their rights under the license."
msgstr ""
"program morate opremiti s kopijo licence GPL, da bodo uporabniki vedeli, kakšne "
"pravice imajo glede uporabe programa,"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/license.rst:33
msgid "You must include the source code or make the source code freely available."
msgstr ""
"k programu morate priložiti izvorno kodo ali jo narediti kako drugače prosto "
"dostopno,"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/license.rst:34
msgid ""
"If you modify the code and distribute the modified version, you must license "
"your modifications available under the GPL (or a compatible license)."
msgstr ""
"če spremenite kodo in širite spremenjeno različico, morate svoje spremembe "
"opremiti z licenco GPL (ali skladno licenco),"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/license.rst:36
msgid ""
"You may not restrict the licensing of the program beyond the terms of the GPL "
"(you may not turn a GPL'd program into a proprietary product)."
msgstr ""
"ne smete omejiti uporabe programa dlje od licence GPL (programa z licenco GPL "
"ne smete spremeniti v lastniški produkt)."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/license.rst:39
msgid ""
"For more on the GPL, check its page on the `GNU Project website <https://www."
"gnu.org/licenses/licenses.html#GPL>`__."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o licenci GPL preberite spletno stran `GNU Project website "
"<https://www.gnu.org/licenses/licenses.html#GPL>`__ (v angleščini)."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/license.rst:44
msgid ""
"The GPL only applies to the Blender application and **not** the artwork you "
"create with it; for more info see the `Blender License <https://www.blender.org/"
"about/license/>`__."
msgstr ""
"Licenca GPL velja samo za program Blender in **ne** velja za umetniška dela, ki "
"jih ustvarite z njim; za več informacij si preberite `Blenderjevo licenco "
"<https://www.blender.org/about/license/>`__."
